{"tha-ap398:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap398:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap398:0.3":"6 Bakulattheraapadana ","tha-ap398:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap398:1.2":"sobhito nama pabbato; ","tha-ap398:1.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap398:1.4":"sakasissehi mapito. ","tha-ap398:2.1":"Mandapa ca bahu tattha, ","tha-ap398:2.2":"pupphita sinduvaraka; ","tha-ap398:2.3":"Kapittha ca bahu tattha, ","tha-ap398:2.4":"pupphita jivajivaka. ","tha-ap398:3.1":"Niggundiyo bahu tattha, ","tha-ap398:3.2":"badaramalakani ca; ","tha-ap398:3.3":"Pharusaka alabu ca, ","tha-ap398:3.4":"pundarika ca pupphita. ","tha-ap398:4.1":"Alaka beluva tattha, ","tha-ap398:4.2":"kadali matulungaka; ","tha-ap398:4.3":"Mahanama bahu tattha, ","tha-ap398:4.4":"ajjuna ca piyanguka. ","tha-ap398:5.1":"Kosamba salala nimba, ","tha-ap398:5.2":"nigrodha ca kapitthana; ","tha-ap398:5.3":"Ediso assamo mayham, ","tha-ap398:5.4":"sasissoham tahim vasim. ","tha-ap398:6.1":"Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap398:6.2":"sayambhu lokanayako; ","tha-ap398:6.3":"Gavesam patisallanam, ","tha-ap398:6.4":"mamassamamupagami. ","tha-ap398:7.1":"Upetamhi mahavire, ","tha-ap398:7.2":"anomadassimahayase; ","tha-ap398:7.3":"Khanena lokanathassa, ","tha-ap398:7.4":"vatabadho samutthahi. ","tha-ap398:8.1":"Vicaranto arannamhi, ","tha-ap398:8.2":"addasam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap398:8.3":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap398:8.4":"cakkhumantam mahayasam. ","tha-ap398:9.1":"Iriyancapi disvana, ","tha-ap398:9.2":"upalakkhesaham tada; ","tha-ap398:9.3":"Asamsayanhi buddhassa, ","tha-ap398:9.4":"byadhi no udapajjatha. ","tha-ap398:10.1":"Khippam assamamaganchim, ","tha-ap398:10.2":"mama sissana santike; ","tha-ap398:10.3":"Bhesajjam kattukamoham, ","tha-ap398:10.4":"sisse amantayim tada. ","tha-ap398:11.1":"Patissunitvana me vakyam, ","tha-ap398:11.2":"sissa sabbe sagarava; ","tha-ap398:11.3":"Ekajjham sannipatimsu, ","tha-ap398:11.4":"satthugaravata mama. ","tha-ap398:12.1":"Khippam pabbatamaruyha, ","tha-ap398:12.2":"sabbosadhamahasaham; ","tha-ap398:12.3":"Paniyayogam katvana, ","tha-ap398:12.4":"buddhasetthassadasaham. ","tha-ap398:13.1":"Paribhutte mahavire, ","tha-ap398:13.2":"sabbannulokanayake; ","tha-ap398:13.3":"Khippam vato vupasami, ","tha-ap398:13.4":"sugatassa mahesino. ","tha-ap398:14.1":"Passaddham daratham disva, ","tha-ap398:14.2":"anomadassi mahayaso; ","tha-ap398:14.3":"Sakasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap398:14.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap398:15.1":"‘Yo me padasi bhesajjam, ","tha-ap398:15.2":"byadhinca samayi mama; ","tha-ap398:15.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap398:15.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap398:16.1":"Kappasatasahassani, ","tha-ap398:16.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap398:16.3":"Vadite turiye tattha, ","tha-ap398:16.4":"modissati sada ayam. ","tha-ap398:17.1":"Manussalokamagantva, ","tha-ap398:17.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap398:17.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap398:17.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap398:18.1":"Pancapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap398:18.2":"anomo nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap398:18.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap398:18.4":"jambumandassa issaro. ","tha-ap398:19.1":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap398:19.2":"cakkavatti mahabbalo; ","tha-ap398:19.3":"Tavatimsepi khobhetva, ","tha-ap398:19.4":"issaram karayissati. ","tha-ap398:20.1":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap398:20.2":"appabadho bhavissati; ","tha-ap398:20.3":"Pariggaham vivajjetva, ","tha-ap398:20.4":"byadhim loke tarissati. ","tha-ap398:21.1":"Apparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap398:21.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap398:21.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap398:21.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap398:22.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap398:22.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap398:22.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap398:22.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap398:23.1":"Kilese jhapayitvana, ","tha-ap398:23.2":"tanhasotam tarissati; ","tha-ap398:23.3":"Bakulo nama namena, ","tha-ap398:23.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap398:24.1":"Idam sabbam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap398:24.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap398:24.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap398:24.4":"etadagge thapessati’. ","tha-ap398:25.1":"Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap398:25.2":"sayambhu lokanayako; ","tha-ap398:25.3":"Vivekanuvilokento, ","tha-ap398:25.4":"mamassamamupagami. ","tha-ap398:26.1":"Upagatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap398:26.2":"sabbannum lokanayakam; ","tha-ap398:26.3":"Sabbosadhena tappesim, ","tha-ap398:26.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap398:27.1":"Tassa me sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap398:27.2":"sukhette bijasampada; ","tha-ap398:27.3":"Khepetum neva sakkomi, ","tha-ap398:27.4":"tada hi sukatam mama. ","tha-ap398:28.1":"Labha mama suladdham me, ","tha-ap398:28.2":"yoham addakkhi nayakam; ","tha-ap398:28.3":"Tena kammavasesena, ","tha-ap398:28.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap398:29.1":"Sabbametam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap398:29.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap398:29.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap398:29.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap398:30.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap398:30.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap398:30.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap398:30.4":"bhesajjassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap398:31.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap398:31.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap398:31.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap398:31.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap398:32.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap398:32.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap398:32.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap398:33.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap398:33.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap398:33.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap398:34.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bakulo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap398:35.1":"Bakulattherassapadanam chattham. "}